"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640716570,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"mwaj50URdtcjKJcr2CgACynjaMF_ulhlNcLeEI0t_4U\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x376975c958069e5326cbf2E6533c8ce2A4Dc8617\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ruAXRUzk4yUE9VKfjYNg9MuvqPoHY5Iq5gagPYptReA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"4aBVy5ZnOMvIFDY7As_k2iKs0cNDFbq2BfWIDVHk0zE\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"6sBa8NJ-BqvY2I9mpu2iRfgtDys4_Ic6Z9PWaeeEDNBS7hwDQMhfnB7hPBo_uAMXbFXDnVfnoGMbLauR8zqHSg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x1f8bddda52aa2408e5842a9e38d5a19825d38890a4bb888e277ffa10f4d2a53a2d726f54521ea4558aa249511c1d6f4e080e5eeef4edfb2efd1aa90c9dcd240e1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ruAXRUzk4yUE9VKfjYNg9MuvqPoHY5Iq5gagPYptReA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"4aBVy5ZnOMvIFDY7As_k2iKs0cNDFbq2BfWIDVHk0zE\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi